text: The news from Florida today is horrific. My heart is with everyone involved in this tragedy. We are all grateful for the men and women in law enforcement and other first-responders for their heroism today.
In regards to the news reports concerning the train crash, Congressman Poliquin was on board, but is okay with a few minor bruises. Please keep your thoughts and prayers with all those affected
